{"tid":2438930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"塭一個同中意又適合同自己過世既人真係好難","createTime":"2021-03-09T01:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:45:59.000Z","uid":382363,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a1628bf6df85713780874c480f87d162961748","tid":2438930,"uid":382363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"感情要兩情相悅<br />\n但總有一方係愛得更多會比較辛苦<br />\n除非2個人本生就好岩傾好夾又想一起拍拖<br />\n就算苦苦成功追到對方但對方可能都處於一種<br />\n唔係好中意你 會騎牛塭馬既心態<br />\n有時候會覺得單身會唔會仲快樂呢<br />\n為自己生活 不用牽掛他人<br />\n<br />\n慢慢我發現左一句金句好岩套用係感情<br />\n「認真就輸了」<br />\n除非一開波大家都肯定認真而呢段感情係自然一起<br />\n又唔會有不對等的付出"},{"pid":"d70be4ab2069f6fc2665f22afed8f2838a5bb0c6","tid":2438930,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:10:29.000Z","msg":"手廿"},{"pid":"a9979468845817fd405befaa77a674446c1f3cbf","tid":2438930,"uid":392319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"有時重要你搵到但人哋已經有另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266440820e09068aa65ead389cd72df5fc5315ad","tid":2438930,"uid":216704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"累了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a3d9f98d26fc28dd051feab8148cb08531a56a","tid":2438930,"uid":366624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:49:25.000Z","msg":"單戀不如不戀"},{"pid":"3730b3700ae24044dd71d92050e3c484defc9522","tid":2438930,"uid":266367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"睇連登真係獲益良多<br />\n睇之前完全想像唔到有人連搵字都打得錯"}]}